[{{es-cluster-name}}] Elasticsearch cluster is unhealthy


@slack-Main_Account-incidents-platform-services , @slack-incidents-platform-services 


{{#is_alert}}
Elasticsearch cluster hasn't been saving snapshots for the past 24 hours.

Follow [the runbook](https://joinhandshake.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/DA/pages/921534749/Student+Incident+Runbook#StudentIncidentRunbook-ElasticsearchClusterfailedtosavesnapshot).

If that doesn't work (should take only a couple seconds), contact ES cloud support for them to resolve the issue.
{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_recovery}}
Elasticsearch Cluster now saves snapshots.
{{/is_recovery}}
